reportData.title: SQL query
reportData.contents:
select rlt.RLTSHP_ID AS RLTSHP_ID,
sub_acc.VNDR_ACCT_ID AS VNDR_ACCT_ID,
sub_acc.ACCT_ID AS ACCT_ID,
sub_acc.BR_NO as BR_NO,
count(distinct sub_acc_type.ACCT_TY_CD) as subAccountTypeCount,
sum(sub_acc_type.ACCT_TY_CD) as subAccountsSum

from PROD.RLTSHP_13120 rlt
join PROD.ACCT_FUNC_GRP_DTL_13088 grp on rlt.ACCT_FUNC_GRP_ID = grp.ACCT_FUNC_GRP_ID
join PROD.SUBACCT_SVC_12569 as sub_acct_svc on grp.ACCT_ID = sub_acct_svc.ACCT_ID
join PROD.SUB_ACCOUNT_12512 as sub_acc on sub_acc.ACCT_ID = sub_acct_svc.ACCT_ID
join PROD.SUBACCT_TYPE_12528 as sub_acc_type on sub_acc.ACCT_ID = sub_acc_type.ACCT_ID
join PROD.ACCOUNT_12280 as acct on acct.ACCT_ID = sub_acct_svc.ACCT_ID
join PROD.ACCT_OWN_RUL_12520 acc_own_rule on acc_own_rule.ACCT_OWN_RULE_ID =  acct.ACCT_OWN_RULE_ID
join PROD.OWN_CLASS_12680 cls on  acc_own_rule.ACCT_OWN_RULE_ID = cls.ACCT_OWN_RULE_ID
join PROD.CONTACT_12250 as contact on contact.CON_ID  = sub_acc.TAX_RPT_CON_ID

where rlt.ISO_CTRY_CD = 'US'
and cls.ACCT_CLASS_CD ='61'
-- and sub_acct_svc.ACTV_IND = 'Y'
-- and sub_acc.AUTH_FORM_IND = 'Y'
and sub_acc.BR_NO = 9979
and sub_acc.ACCT_CLS_UT is NULL
and sub_acc.acct_rst_ind = 'N'
-- and sub_acct_svc.ACCT_SVC_TY_CD='SE'
--owner is not deceased
and contact.DEATH_DA is null
--inherited = N
-- and acct.dcdnt_retr_ind = 'N'
-- and acct.ACCT_ACTV_IND='N'
 and sub_acc.ACCT_ID in (
select
sub_acc.ACCT_ID AS ACCT_ID

from PROD.SUB_ACCOUNT_12512 as sub_acc
join PROD.ACCT_RLTD_PY_12310 as rol on rol.ACCT_ID=sub_acc.ACCT_ID
join PROD.CONTACT_12250 as con on con.CON_ID = rol.RLTD_CON_ID
join PROD.ACCOUNT_12280 as acct on acct.ACCT_ID = sub_acc.ACCT_ID
join PROD.ACCT_OWN_RUL_12520 acc_own_rule on acc_own_rule.ACCT_OWN_RULE_ID =  acct.ACCT_OWN_RULE_ID
join PROD.OWN_CLASS_12680 cls on  acc_own_rule.ACCT_OWN_RULE_ID = cls.ACCT_OWN_RULE_ID

where sub_acc.ACCT_CLS_UT is NULL
and sub_acc.acct_rst_ind='N'
and sub_acc.BR_NO = 9979
and con.DEATH_DA is null
and rol.LGCL_DEL_DA is NULL
and rol.CON_RLSHP_TY_CD in ('AUTH','CNTRLPRSN','COMM','CONSV','CURATOR','CUST','GRDN','OWNROLE','TTEE','TUTOR','POA')
and cls.ACCT_CLASS_CD ='61'

group by sub_acc.ACCT_ID
having count(distinct rol.CON_RLSHP_TY_CD)>=2
)

and sub_acc.acct_id not in
(               select a.acct_id
                from
                    PROD.ACCOUNT_12280 a
                    left outer join PROD.acct_rst_10214 v on v.account_no= a.cust_no
                    inner join PROD.ACCT_OWN_RUL_12520 acc_own_rule on acc_own_rule.ACCT_OWN_RULE_ID =  a.ACCT_OWN_RULE_ID
                    inner join PROD.OWN_CLASS_12680 cls on  acc_own_rule.ACCT_OWN_RULE_ID =  cls.ACCT_OWN_RULE_ID
                    inner join PROD.SUB_ACCOUNT_12512 as sub_acc on sub_acc.ACCT_ID=a.ACCT_ID
                where
                    v.rst_rsn_cd is not null
                    and v.rst_rsn_cd in ('AUTH', 'DOCU', 'WARN', 'CIPR', 'COPD', 'CO', 'RISK', 'SSN', 'FTRN', '72T', 'MISC', 'MAIL', 'FOR', 'FOR2', 'R471', 'R407','DEATH')
                    and cls.ACCT_CLASS_CD ='61'
                    and sub_acc.BR_NO = 9979
                    and a.ACCT_CLS_DA is null
)
group by rlt.RLTSHP_ID, sub_acc.VNDR_ACCT_ID, sub_acc.ACCT_ID, sub_acc.BR_NO
having sum(sub_acc_type.ACCT_TY_CD) >= 1
fetch first 500 rows only;

reportData.title: SQL query
reportData.contents:
SELECT 
    L.ACCT_ID, 
    L.CON_ID, 
    L.LGCL_DEL_DA,
    L.ACCT_ROLE_CD, 
    L.CON_RLSHP_TY_CD, 
    K.LOC_ACCT_ROLE_NA,
    
    D.FST_GVN_NA,
    D.MID_GVN_NA,
    D.MAIN_FAM_NA,
    C.EMAIL_ADR_TXT,
    B.DEATH_DA

FROM

(
    SELECT 
        A.IR_NO, A.ACCT_ID, B.ACCT_ROLE_CD, A.CON_ID, A.ACCT_SEQ_NO,
        A.CON_DATA_COMPL_IND, A.LGCL_DEL_DA, CAST (NULL AS CHAR (1)) AS ACCT_PRTY_APP_STAT_CD,
        CAST (NULL AS CHAR (1)) AS ACCT_PRTY_APP_EMPL_ID, CAST (NULL AS DATE) AS ACCT_PRTY_APP_DA,
        CAST (NULL AS CHAR (1)) AS CON_RLSHP_TY_CD, CAST (NULL AS CHAR (1)) AS ACCT_PRTY_BUS_TITLE_CD,
        CAST (NULL AS CHAR (1)) AS W9_RCV_IND
    FROM 
        PROD.CUST_ACCT_12281 AS A, 
        PROD.ACCTROLEXREF_10099 AS B
    WHERE 
        A.ACCT_ID = 143469836 
        AND A.ACCT_ROLE_CD = B.LGCY_ACCT_ROLE_CD AND A.LGCL_DEL_DA IS NULL

    UNION ALL
    
    SELECT 
        IR_NO, ACCT_ID, ACCT_ROLE_CD, CON_ID, ACCT_SEQ_NO, 'Y' AS CON_DATA_COMPL_IND,
        LGCL_DEL_DA, CAST (NULL AS CHAR (1)) AS ACCT_PRTY_APP_STAT_CD,
        CAST (NULL AS CHAR (1)) AS ACCT_PRTY_APP_EMPL_ID, CAST (NULL AS DATE) AS ACCT_PRTY_APP_DA,
        CAST (NULL AS CHAR (1)) AS CON_RLSHP_TY_CD, CAST (NULL AS CHAR (1)) AS ACCT_PRTY_BUS_TITLE_CD, W9_RCV_IND
    FROM 
        PROD.CLNT_SACCT_12553 AS C 
    WHERE 
        ACCT_ID = 143469836 
        AND LGCL_DEL_DA IS NULL

    UNION ALL
    
    SELECT 
        D.CON_PART_KEY AS IR_NO, D.ACCT_ID, E.ACCT_ROLE_CD, D.RLTD_CON_ID AS CON_ID, D.ACCT_SEQ_NO,
        D.CON_DATA_COMPL_IND, D.LGCL_DEL_DA, D.ACCT_PRTY_APP_STAT_CD, D.ACCT_PRTY_APP_EMPL_ID, D.ACCT_PRTY_APP_DA,
        D.CON_RLSHP_TY_CD, D.ACCT_PRTY_BUS_TITLE_CD, CAST (NULL AS CHAR (1)) AS W9_RCV_IND
    FROM 
        PROD.ACCT_RLTD_PY_12310 AS D, PROD.ACCTROLEXREF_10099 AS E
    WHERE 
        D.ACCT_ID = 143469836 
        AND D.CON_RLSHP_TY_CD = E.LGCY_ACCT_ROLE_CD AND D.LGCL_DEL_DA IS NULL

    UNION ALL
    
    SELECT 
        IR_NO, ACCT_ID, ACCT_ROLE_CD, CON_ID, ACCT_SEQ_NO, CON_DATA_COMPL_IND, LGCL_DEL_DA,
        CAST (NULL AS CHAR (1)) AS ACCT_PRTY_APP_STAT_CD, CAST (NULL AS CHAR (1)) AS ACCT_PRTY_APP_EMPL_ID,
        CAST (NULL AS DATE) AS ACCT_PRTY_APP_DA, CAST (NULL AS CHAR (1)) AS CON_RLSHP_TY_CD,
        CAST (NULL AS CHAR (1)) AS ACCT_PRTY_BUS_TITLE_CD, W9_RCV_IND
    FROM 
        PROD.SACC_AUTH_PY_12548 AS O
    WHERE 
        ACCT_ID = 143469836 
        AND LGCL_DEL_DA IS NULL
) AS L

LEFT OUTER JOIN PROD.LOC_ACCTROLE_12610 AS K ON L.ACCT_ROLE_CD = K.ACCT_ROLE_CD AND K.ISO_CTRY_CD = 'US'
LEFT JOIN PROD.CON_NAME_12284 D ON L.CON_ID = D.CON_ID
LEFT JOIN PROD.CON_EMAIL_13899 A ON A.CON_ID = L.CON_ID
LEFT JOIN PROD.EMAIL_ADR_13898 C ON C.EMAIL_ID = A.EMAIL_ID
LEFT JOIN PROD.CONTACT_12250 B on B.CON_ID = L.CON_ID
